                            <comment id="13426956" author="cheolsoo" created="Wed, 1 Aug 2012 23:17:02 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached is a patch that changes the name of the method in PigAvroDatumWriter from resolveUnion() to resolveUnionSchema() to avoid the conflict.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I tested against Avro 1.5.3, 1.6.3, and 1.7.1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13427070" author="sms" created="Thu, 2 Aug 2012 02:56:03 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 looks good. I will commit it after running the tests.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13427081" author="sms" created="Thu, 2 Aug 2012 03:44:20 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch has been committed to trunk. I tested the changes for both Hadoop 20 and Hadoop 23. There are unrelated failure in TestDBStorage (20 and 23) and TestMultiStorage (23)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks Cheolsoo!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
